name: Oscar Isaac
description:
Óscar Isaac Hernández Estrada (born March 9, 1979) is a Guatemalan-born American actor. Known for his versatility, he has been credited with breaking stereotypes about Latino characters in Hollywood.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Today, I am happy to present a textual inversion of Oscar Isaac! Every feedback is welcome as usual! I used 30 public images of him, 3000 steps. To use it:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder

  • Then simply add osisaac to your prompt and enjoy!

  • Keep the Samples around 30, and CFG around 8, but feel free to experiment!
